	(40,45,'Amazon','B00OHY14CS','','Anonymous User','August Smart Lock - Keyless Home Entry with Your Smartphone','august-smart-lock','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The August Smart Lock is a device that connects to your deadbolt and connects to bluetooth, allowing you to control, lock and unlock your door, all from your phone, eliminating both the worry of forgetting your key at home, while also cutting back on the amount of things you need to carry around with you on a daily basis. Additionally, this is the only current smart lock on the market that doesn‚Äôt require you to entirely replace your current lock system, and is in fact designed to work with the deadbolt you already have installed. In short, this is a great product, with users claiming that it has a lot of potential and is following a great idea. It is also important to note however, that users claim there are still connectivity issues and give it a 3 out of 5 possible stars overall.</span></p><ul><ul><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">Smart lock that allows you to lock/unlock doors via your phone</span></li><li class=\"li1\">Blue tooth capabilities¬†</li><li class=\"li1\">Works with almost all existing locking systems, eliminating the need to replace them in order to use the product</li></ul><br/></ul><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>','[{\"key\":\"Manufacturer\",\"value\":\"August\"},{\"key\":\"Model\",\"value\":\"ASL-1\"},{\"key\":\"Part Number\",\"value\":\"TY0918\"},{\"key\":\"Color\",\"value\":\"Silver\"},{\"key\":\"Product Size\",\"value\":\"2.21 X 3.26 X 3.26 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Package Size\",\"value\":\"2.5 X 5 X 9 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Weight\",\"value\":\"1 Pound\"}]',299.99,144.99,1,'http://www.amazon.com/August-Smart-Lock-Keyless-Smartphone/dp/B00OHY14CS%3Fpsc%3D1%26SubscriptionId%3DAKIAIQYICLTUI4NBTPGA%26tag%3Dideaing07-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB00OHY14CS','','[{\"key\":\"Average\",\"value\":\"4.00\",\"counter\":1},{\"key\":\"Amazon\",